                           Project 2 - Combinational chips
                           ----------------------- 
  

Submitted Files
---------------
README - This file.
Inc16.hdl - 6-bit incrementer: out = in + 1 (arithmetic addition)
HalfAdder.hdl - Computes the sum of two bits.
fullAdder.hdl - Computes the sum of three bits.
Add16.hdl - Adds two 16-bit values.
ShiftLef.hdl - multiply number by 2.
ShiftRight.hdl - divide number by 2.
Mul.hdl - multiply two numbers.
ALU.hdl - complete Arithmetic Logic Unit.

